<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1 class="card-header">About Me</h1>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-4">
              <%= image_tag "profile-image.jpg", alt: "Profile Image", width: '100%' %>

              <div class="skills">
                <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                  <div class="skill">
                    <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                    <div class="progress">
                      <div
                        class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                        role="progressbar"
                        aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                        aria-valuemax="100"
                        style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                      >
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                <% end %>
              </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-md-8">
              <p class="lead">
                  With several years of experience in creating websites and helping businesses grow online I would love to do the same for you. Most people view their business website as a "virtual business card". That's true, but only if you view it as just a website. I transform your website into an effective online marketing channel.
              </p>

              <p class="lead">
                  When I take on a project not only do I work to craft the application according to the client's specifications, I give daily updates to ensure that the project is aligning properly with the client's goals. The end result is the right product, delivered on time, and on budget.
              </p>

              <p>
                <button
                  class="btn btn-primary"
                  type="button"
                  data-toggle="collapse"
                  data-target="#jobHistory"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controller="jobHistory"
                >
                  Clients
                </button>

                <button
                  class="btn btn-primary"
                  type="button"
                  data-toggle="collapse"
                  data-target="#testimonials"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controller="testimonials"
                >
                  Testimonials
                </button>

                <p>
                  <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
                    <div class="card card-block bg-light">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-text">
                          Art Life Images
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card card-block">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-text">
                          Your Hearts Dream Wedding
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>


                    <div class="card card-block bg-light">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-text">
                          CoreVision Media
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="card card-block">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-text">
                          The Hostess With The Mostest
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  <div class="collapse" id="testimonials">
                    <div class="card card-block bg-light">
                      <div class="card-body">
                        <div class="card-text">
                          <blockquote>
                            David takes your ideas and makes them better. He does an amazing job with web design! He's very easy to work with. He's always quick to respond and very professional. I couldn't be happier with my website.
                            <cite>
                              - Karin R. Owner of Art Life Images
                            </cite>
                          </blockquote>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </p>
              </p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>






